<dl>
    <dt>Go to the People lens</dt>
    <dt>Select a contact from the carousel</dt>
        <dd>Contact's summary shall be displayed</dd>
        <dd>Accessing the phone number raises the Phone application in the Dialer pane</dd>
        <dd>Accessing the phone number through the message icon raises the Phone application in the Conversations pane</dd>
        <dd>Summary can be dismissed by accessing the lower region of the screen</dd>
    <dt>Input search text for contacts known to be found</dt>
        <dd>The lens shall filter the content with matching items</dd>
    <dt>Select the matching contact</dt>
        <dd>Contact's summary shall be displayed</dd>
        <dd>Summary can be dismissed by accessing the lower region of the screen</dd>
    <dt>Dismiss the search</dt>
        <dd>The lens' unfiltered view shall be rendered</dd>
</dl>
<strong>If all actions produce the expected results listed, please <a href="results#add_result">submit</a> a 'passed' result.
    If an action fails, or produces an unexpected result, please <a href="results#add_result">submit</a> a 'failed' result and <a href="../../buginstructions">file a bug</a>. Please be sure to include the bug number when you <a href="results#add_result">submit</a> your result.</strong>
